column4:
We rely on the #PostalService to conduct business, get prescription medications, critical supplies, &amp; exercise our right to vote. 

@HouseDemocrats are taking action this week to protect the postal service and our democracy from Trump’s sabotage. (1/2)

#DontMessWithUSPS

Trump: “The Republican party will be known as the party of healthcare.” 

Reality: His administration is in court today trying to have Obamacare, including coverage of pre-existing conditions, ruled unconstitutional. 

@HouseDemocrats will continue to fight to #ProtectOurCare.
